Package it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.map

Class Block

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.map.Block
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cell
public class Block
extends java.lang.Object
implements Cell
Class that represents a block, the concrete object described by the cell

It contains its current and previous level, its coordinates (x and y) and the eventual pawn that can be on this block
